summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2008 NISSAN VERSA. UPON STARTING THE VEHICLE, THE AIR BAG INDICATOR ILLUMINATED. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO NISSAN OF BURLINGAME (101 CALIFORNIA DR, BURLINGAME, CA 94010). THE DEALER STATED THAT THEY COULD NOT COMPLETE THE RECALL REPAIR FOR NHTSA CAMPAIGN NUMBER: 16V349000 (AIR BAGS) UNTIL THE UNKNOWN FAILURE THAT CAUSED THE AIR BAG INDICATOR TO ILLUMINATE COULD BE REPAIRED. A DIAGNOSTIC TEST WOULD ALSO BE NEEDED. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT DIAGNOSED OR REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURE. THE APPROXIMATE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 80,000.
